---
---

<section class="bg-white py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="animate-on-scroll text-orange font-bold text-sm tracking-widest mb-4" data-animation="fade-in">PROBLEM</p>
      <h2 class="animate-on-scroll text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-navy leading-tight" data-animation="fade-up">
        経営者が抱える「高コスト」と「孤立」の壁
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Cost wall -->
      <div class="animate-on-scroll bg-gray-light rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10" data-animation="slide-left">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-navy/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-black text-navy">コストの壁</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-dark/80">
          <p>一般的な経営コンサルタントの顧問料相場：</p>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4">
            <p class="font-bold text-navy">月額 <span class="font-accent text-2xl">20</span>〜<span class="font-accent text-2xl">40</span>万円</p>
            <p class="text-sm mt-1">1日あたり<span class="font-accent font-bold">2</span>〜<span class="font-accent font-bold">4</span>万円</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
            多くの中小企業にとって、<br />
            継続的な指導を受けることは大きな負担に。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Practice wall -->
      <div class="animate-on-scroll bg-gray-light rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10" data-animation="slide-right">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-navy/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728A9 9 0 015.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-black text-navy">実践の壁</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-dark/80">
          <p>「問題を自覚していても…」</p>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4">
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-orange mt-0.5">&#10005;</span>
                <span>外部の人間に相談できず孤立</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-orange mt-0.5">&#10005;</span>
                <span>書籍と認めるだけでは成果にならない</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-orange mt-0.5">&#10005;</span>
                <span>実行に移すための伴走者がいない</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">
            受けっぱなしの研修では、<br />
            成果につながりません。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
